supports the OAuth 2.0 Authorization Code Grant.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 RedirectUris => ArrayRef[Str|Undef]

A list of URIs that are valid locations to redirect a user's browser
after the user is authorized.

RedirectUris is required when the grant type is C<authorization_code>.



